`_forward_action` routes based on the blocked role (lines 135-148):

| Blocked role | Escalates to |
|-------------|-------------|
| Boss | Taskmaster (window 1, pane 0) |
| Worker | Subtaskmaster (same window, pane 0) |
| Coordinator | First worker team (window 2, pane 0) |
| Team Lead | Taskmaster (window 1, pane 0) |
| Other | Same window, pane 0 |

